    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m absolutely in love with this car, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's basically spotless inside and out. You won't find another one this pristine. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it as much as I do!",
