    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours-level condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 power unit, boasting six individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagement, paired with a meticulously maintained variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. Critically, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the double-VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The rod bearing service is documented, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications. This is a turn-key, mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning collector who demands uncompromising performance and structural integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "One owner. Garage kept. Zero accidents. Full service history included. Pristine interior and exterior. Drives like new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
