      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true showroom masterpiece, preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirls, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh condition; the premium leather is soft and free of creases, the carpets are spotless, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service log documenting every scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. Every button, sensor, and feature functions as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that looks, feels, and drives like it just left the dealership floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
