    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it\u2019s basically like new! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it\u2019s still got that fresh feel and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for something pristine and ready for the road, this is the one! \u2728",
