    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2004 BMW M3, a benchmark in naturally aspirated performance. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS variable valve timing that operates with surgical precision. This unit is mated to a factory Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, providing tactile engagement through every gear. The chassis remains structurally flawless, with a verified intact rear subframe and pristine bushings. The M-variable differential lock provides optimal torque distribution, while the factory suspension maintains its original damping rate. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior exhibits a deep luster with zero signs of oxidation or road rash. The interior features Nappa leather with no bolster wear, and all electronics function within original factory specifications. This is a collector-grade example for the enthusiast who demands mechanical integrity and historical purity.",
